    "description": "Experience the ultimate survival horror adventure with ASTRAL - Dream Or Reality! Step into the shoes of Adam and immerse yourself in a world full of puzzles and dangers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831610/extras/e04f9ae2624253ffe6ce1d580679bcf0.avif?t=1685970488\" width=800 height=162 /></span><br><br>Survive in a world teeming with obstacles and perils by not only managing your stamina but also keeping an eye on your psyche. <br>Find useful items to stay alive or avoid excessive stress. <br>But beware: every decision you make influences the course of the story and can determine life or death.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831610/extras/5abb4896463bdff9579cdb3ac2a0acaf.avif?t=1685970488\" width=800 height=150 /></span><br><br>Prepare yourself for a gripping narrative that will keep you captivated until the end. <br>As Adam, you will start with an ordinary evening that quickly turns into a true horror trip. <br>Will you uncover the truth and solve the mystery surrounding Kara and the enigmatic house, or will you venture down the wrong path, sealing your own fate?<br><br><br>And the best part is: ASTRAL - Dream Or Reality will receive free DLCs and content updates, continuously expanding and enhancing the game. <br>Do you dare to embark on this adventure?",
